opam-version: "2.0"
name: "travis-opam"
version: "1.2.0"
synopsis: "Scripts for OCaml projects"
description: """
Supported CI:

- **stable**: [Travis CI](/README-travis.md) Ubuntu, Debian and OSX workers.
- **experimental**: [Appveyor](/README-appveyor.md) Windows Server 2012 R2 (x64) workers."""
